description:
As a job seeker
  I want to apply for jobs
  So that I can have a chance to get a job
name: Apply with Resume

elements.name: Existing member with resume can start apply

steps.name: I am logged in to an account with resume
I should see Logged In Header module
I should land on Search Result page
I click to View the 2nd Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page
I should land on Apply page

elements.name: Existing member with resume can submit application by clicking Send button

steps.name: I am logged in to an account with resume
I should see Logged In Header module
I should land on Search Result page
I click to View the 2nd Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page
I should land on Apply page
I should land on Apply Success page

elements.name: Existing member with resume can choose resume

steps.name: I am logged in to an account with resume
I should see Logged In Header module
I should land on Search Result page
I click to View the 2nd Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page
I should land on Apply page
I select UploadResume from Resume dropdown list

description:
As a job seeker
  I want to apply for jobs
  So that I can have a chance to get a job
name: Apply without Resume

elements.name: Existing member without resume cannot start apply

steps.name: I am logged in to an account without resume
I should see Logged In Header module
I should land on Search Result page
I click to View the 1st Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page
I should land on Complete Your Profile page
I should see App Store button

description:
As a job seeker
  I want to login
  So that I can use the features for logged in members
name: Login

elements.name: Existing member cannot login with incorrect email & password

steps.name: I type in carrielai@seekasia.com on email field
I type in WrongPassword on password field
Alert pops up: Either the user name or password was entered incorrectly, please try again.

elements.name: User can go to create an account from Login page

steps.name: I should land on Sign Up page

elements.name: User can go to Forgot password page from Login page

steps.name: I should land on Forgot Password page

description:
As a job seeker
  After I search for jobs,
  I want to browse around the results
  So that I can view more jobs
name: Search Result

elements.name: View job ad

steps.name: I should land on Search Result page
I click to View the 1st Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page

elements.name: Go to next page

steps.name: I should land on Search Result page
I should land on Search Result page

elements.name: User need to login before saving a job

steps.name: I should land on Search Result page
I click to Save the 1st Job Ad
I should land on Login page

elements.name: User can login when saving a job and go back to Search result page

steps.name: I should land on Search Result page
I click to Save the 1st Job Ad
I should land on Login page
I am logged in to an account

description:

  I want to search for jobs
  So that I can see new posted jobs

The Search Criteria should contain all jobs

steps.name: I type in QA Analyst on Keyword field

elements.name: Search by job function ( level one job function )

steps.name: I select Accounting from Job function dropdown list
I should land on Search Result page
The Search Criteria should contain Accounting
